id Austin Walsh)。 （对于那些不知道的人来说，博士后职位是一种低薪炼狱，拥有博士学位的人在无法立即获得教授职位时被派去继续进行研究。）沃尔什是<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Taking-America-Back-Conservative-Movement/dp/0300260970">最近发布的</a>一本书的作者<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Taking-America-Back-Conservative-Movement/dp/0300260970">书</a><em>《夺回美国：保守派运动和极右翼</em>》，但他最出名的身份是推特上直言不讳且固执己见的评论员。当我的播客联合主持人布拉德·德隆 (Brad DeLong)<a href="https://x.com/delong/status/1100157177816379395">在 2019 年宣布</a>，像他这样的新自由主义者是时候将接力棒“传递给更左翼的同事”时，他引用了沃尔什的一条推文。近年来，沃尔什花了很多时间从左翼角度攻击乔·拜登。自加沙战争开始以来，这些袭击变得更加猛烈。</p><p>但这并不是让 Twitter（或者现在正式称为 X）今天感到兴奋的原因。相反，沃尔什宣称，他未能获得终身教职的学术工作至少部分是由于他是白人这一事实： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F30583334-4fcb-48a4-b823-807cfb532eb8_1059x738.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_pr